Jeffrey D. Stearman – Attorney at Law
Attorney Stearman has been practicing law since 1982 and is currently a member in good standing with the California State Bar, as well being a member of the Orange County Bar (including the FAMILY LAW section) and Los Angeles County Bar Associations. He is licensed to practice law in all state courts throughout the State of California, as well as in the United States Central District Court.
We currently serve clients in Orange County. 
So, if you are seeking an HONEST, FAIR ATTORNEY with INTEGRITY, contact Attorney JEFFREY D. STEARMAN now for your FREE INITIAL CONSULTATION.
Call 714-871-7778 or Email our office.





