Firm Overview
Handling most legal matters in Orange County,  California since 1982.
Many law firms, particularly the large ones, make extensive use of case managers to handle client cases - individuals employed by a firm not licensed to practice law. A large part of our success on behalf of our clients is due to the PERSONAL HANDLING AND ATTENTION of your case from start to finish and our availability and accessibility to our clients, including PROMPT RETURN OF TELEPHONE CALLS. 
 
If you have a legal case in Southern California, we can help.
Call for a Free Consultation
Contact my office today to personally discuss your family law questions. You can call 714-871-7778 for a FREE initial phone consultation or send me an email. I am available by phone during regular business hours and regularly check email evenings and weekends.
We Accept Credit Cards





Jeffrey Stearman
