#22,805 in weekly profile views out of 284,731 total Law Firms Overall
                      










 







About our 
                            Huntington Beach, CA:
                            office


                Law Office of Jeffrey D. Stearman handles most legal matters in Orange County, California since 1982. We are a full service law firm dedicated to providing you with prompt, AFFORDABLE service, handling most legal matters. From Family Law, Dissolution, Divorce, Custody, Child Support, Spousal Support, Legal Separation, Contempt, Domestic Violence, Restraining Orders, Paternity, Criminal Defense, DUI, Traffic Tickets, Personal Injury, Product Liability, Dog Bites, Slip & Falls, Collections, Contracts, Corporation Formation and General Civil Litigation we can help you. Many law firms, particularly the large ones, make extensive use of case managers to handle client cases-individuals employed by a firm not licensed to practice law. A large part of our success on behalf of our clients is due to the personal handling and attention of your case from start to finish and our availability and accessibility to our clients, including prompt return of telephone calls. If you have a case in Southern California, we can help.
            





