About Law Office of Jeffrey D. Stearman




                    Free Initial Consultation. Quality representation at affordable rates. After successfully practicing law for over 30 years, Attorney Jeffrey Stearman in Huntington Beach, CA. is the "go to" attorney!Law Office of Jeffrey D. Stearman handles most legal matters in Orange County, California since 1982. We are a full service law firm dedicated to providing you with prompt, AFFORDABLE service, handling most legal matters. From Family Law, Diss...
                    Read more


                    Free Initial Consultation. Quality representation at affordable rates. After successfully practicing law for over 30 years, Attorney Jeffrey Stearman in Huntington Beach, CA. is the "go to" attorney!Law Office of Jeffrey D. Stearman handles most legal matters in Orange County, California since 1982. We are a full service law firm dedicated to providing you with prompt, AFFORDABLE service, handling most legal matters. From Family Law, Dissolution, Divorce, Custody, Child Support, Spousal Support, Legal Separation, Contempt, Domestic Violence, Restraining Orders, Paternity, Criminal Defense, DUI, Traffic Tickets, Personal Injury, Product Liability, Dog Bites, Slip & Falls, Collections, Contracts, Corporation Formation and General Civil Litigation we can help you. Many law firms, particularly the large ones, make extensive use of case managers to handle client cases-individuals employed by a firm not licensed to practice law. A large part of our success on behalf of our clients is due to the personal handling and attention of your case from start to finish and our availability and accessibility to our clients, including prompt return of telephone calls. If you have a case in Southern California, we can help.
                    Read less


